<div id="review_11776627" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/11776627" />
    <a title="Alison" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/746793-alison"><img alt="Alison" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1380201542p2/746793.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/11776627?book_show_action=true">Jan 06, 2008</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Alison" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Alison" href="/user/show/746793-alison">Alison</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="did not like it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">did not like it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>


          <div><span class="uitext greyText">Recommends it for: </span>
           <span class="uitext reviewText">Fans of M. Night Shyalaman who pretend to read philosopher before pilates class.</span></div>

        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer11776627" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2850419428594064118">I&apos;m tired of the super-twist endings and the ponderous philosophical musings on guilt and morality. I&apos;m tired of successful, monied people in nicely renovated townhouses feeling sorry for themselves. Maybe I don&apos;t get Ian McEwan. I&apos;m okay with that. But I&apos;m not going to read another one of these.</span>
  <span id="freeText2850419428594064118" style="display:none">I'm tired of the super-twist endings and the ponderous philosophical musings on guilt and morality. I'm tired of successful, monied people in nicely renovated townhouses feeling sorry for themselves. Maybe I don't get Ian McEwan. I'm okay with that. But I'm not going to read another one of these.</span>
  <a data-text-id="2850419428594064118" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
