        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2180092303" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10398692011876299580">A novella rather than a full length book, this was a very quick read. It’s my first McEwan and I didn’t know what to expect. I enjoyed the black humour and the satire - vaguely reminiscent of Muriel Spark but not so clever - and some of the writing is excellent. I thought the premise of the book and the ending were silly though. It just pushes itself into 4 stars because it’s made me want to read more of this author’s work and I did generally enjoy it.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


